  <name>Workout Timer</name>
  <summary>Round timer and workout planner</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A sport training application for Linux. Features a configurable round timer
      with pause periods and audio alerts, a training plan builder with multi-round
      circuit support, and an AI coach for generating personalized plans.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Home page with quick access to recent and recommended workouts</li>
      <li>Configurable round timer with adjustable rounds, duration, and pause</li>
      <li>Training plan builder with timed and rep-based exercises</li>
      <li>Multi-round circuits with configurable rest between rounds</li>
      <li>AI coach for generating training plans with local or cloud LLMs</li>
      <li>Built-in exercise database with 873 exercises and images</li>
      <li>11 pre-built default training plans, including pop culture-inspired workouts</li>
      <li>Training history with per-exercise logging and CSV export/import</li>
      <li>Customizable sound effects for different events</li>
      <li>Fullscreen mode for workout sessions</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
